text: Anna Marie Höljer-Serra (born 22 October 1965) is a road cyclist from Sweden. She represented her nation at the 1988 Summer Olympics in the women's road race and at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Swedish female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Sweden Category:Living people Category:People from Västmanland County Category:1965 births
